title: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: When exporting data from the attached report, an exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() function.
OB: When attempting to export the data in a table that contains highlights or a map, an exception is thrown in the report engine service.
EB: Data should be exported successfully from tables, even if they contain highlights or a map.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Export the data from a table that contains highlights or a map.
3. Observe that an exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() function.
